<main class="min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <.link
          href={~p"/about"}
          class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"
            />
          </svg>
          {gettext("Back to About")}
        </.link>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-base-content mb-8">
        {gettext("About Tango")}
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
            {gettext("The People Behind This App")}
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext("This application was created by")} <b>Tango</b>{gettext(
              ", together with our AI-powered virtual team member,"
            )} <b>Claudete</b>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "Tango is a Canada-based software company focused on building modern, scalable digital products by combining cutting-edge technology with AI-assisted development. We help organizations move faster, build smarter, and deliver higher-quality software without unnecessary complexity."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <b>Claudete</b> {gettext("was born from our hands-on work with two AI tools —")}
            <b>Claude Code</b> {gettext("and")} <b>Tidewave</b>{gettext(
              ". Their combined strengths evolved into a collaborative virtual team member that works alongside our developers, accelerating delivery while maintaining precision and quality."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "What began as an internal learning journey—exploring the real-world potential of AI-assisted development—quickly became something more. As we experienced the impact firsthand, we realized how powerful it is to put AI directly into the hands of experienced engineers. The results reshaped how we think about software delivery."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "We saw possibilities not just for startups, but for development teams of any size—across private and public sectors, and in virtually any industry."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "While many large organizations attempt to improve outcomes by measuring productivity, our experience shows that true gains come from"
            )}
            <i>{gettext("speed")}</i>, <i>{gettext("accuracy")}</i>, {gettext("and")}
            <i>{gettext("quality")}</i>{gettext(
              ". With AI as a true collaborator, those metrics are no longer incremental—they're transformed."
            )}
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
            {gettext("Our Mission")}
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <b>{gettext("Build what's next. Together.")}</b>
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "AI-powered development, seasoned engineers, and technical coaching for modern software teams."
            )}
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-4">
            {gettext("Work With Us")}
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "At Tango, we don't just build products — we help teams rethink how software gets delivered in an AI-first world."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "Whether you're exploring AI-assisted development, modernizing existing systems, or building something entirely new, we partner closely with your team to turn ideas into high-quality, production-ready solutions. Our approach blends experienced engineers with AI-powered workflows to deliver results faster, with greater accuracy and long-term maintainability."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-2">
            {gettext("We work with:")}
          </p>
          <ul class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4 ml-4 list-disc">
            <li>{gettext("Startups looking to move fast without sacrificing quality")}</li>
            <li>{gettext("Established companies modernizing their development practices")}</li>
            <li>
              {gettext("Public and private sector teams tackling complex technical challenges")}
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            {gettext(
              "If you're curious about how AI can elevate your development process — or you need a trusted partner to help build, scale, or innovate — we'd love to collaborate."
            )}
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
            <b>{gettext("Let's build what's next, together.")}</b>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-base-300">
        <.link
          href={~p"/about"}
          class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"
            />
          </svg>
          {gettext("Back to About")}
        </.link>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
